{"tid":49933,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"19歲卜卜脆　徐嬌騷長腿晒女人味","createTime":"2016-12-22T05:19:04.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T05:44:31.000Z","uid":31314,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ee3533f23ac549c72a7d8a56490d65b064e70f8e","tid":49933,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T05:19:04.000Z","msg":"女大十八變！大陸女星徐嬌於2008年以童星身份與周星馳合演電影瞬間爆紅，但她在2013年決定赴美國求學，當時曾被指不懂珍惜機會，她出席活動時表示毫不後悔留學的決定：「現在的我，做一切我想做的事，誰說20歲的女生不知道自己想要甚麼？」<br />\n<br />\n原來她赴美求學之前的成績相當優異，一共被美國4間名校錄取，學成歸來，已經19歲的徐嬌出席活動時艷麗難掩，她身穿黑色吊帶裙現身，坐在高櫈上大騷白皙長腿，身材纖瘦，愈長愈漂亮，初顯女人味！<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/k1rf9nha\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fk1rf9nha&h=ed2e9aa2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2dd12d277240dc8fe9f404c8e8dc4ceea33b45c","tid":49933,"uid":2155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T05:20:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4e39e19073fba8c7e4639fcd34517c422860a24","tid":49933,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T05:21:01.000Z","msg":"對腳又老又唔滑"},{"pid":"af367ad42023d1754e920daff94a86736deb4f68","tid":49933,"uid":8636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T05:21:15.000Z","msg":"YOU"},{"pid":"a537a50c6d02a142079520746313e89905b57711","tid":49933,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T05:21:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對腳又老又唔滑</blockquote><br />\n蓋ching食開屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddb9c8742d08af45ab5a24122cc661e06d6ff279","tid":49933,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T05:22:09.000Z","msg":"人生有污點"},{"pid":"f97eb2cb215d7634116ede88bbbaa8d39a7d6b85","tid":49933,"uid":14441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T05:22:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>YOU</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n竟"},{"pid":"2e6bdfc8709a79